elements.name: To verify that the System admin is able to Add telco operator through user management module.

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin Maker
Navigate to User Management and Click on register
Select User type as Business and click on Telco operator
Enter all the mandatory Basic information details and click on next
Enter all the mandatory Profile details like marketing profile,regulatory profile,Operator profile.
Click on Next >> click on Confirm
Confirmation message
Logout
Login into Mobiquity Portal as another System admin Checker1 after logout
Navigate to Approvals and filter by Submitted status
User click on submitted user data
Approve the Users

elements.name: To verify that the System admin is able to Modify  telco operator through user management module.

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin Maker
Navigate to User Management and Click on manage user
Enter Telco operator Mobile number and KYC number in search menu
User Click on eye button
Click on edit
Edit the required details >> Click on Next
Click on save
Confirmation modify message
Logout
Login into Mobiquity Portal as another System admin Checker1 after logout
Navigate to Approvals and filter by Submitted status
User click on submitted user data
Approve the Users
